parameters.query:
SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct br.id, 
b.ref_no, 
to_char(b.request_start_at::timestamp,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') as trip_start, 
to_char(b.request_end_at::timestamp,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') as trip_end, 
bra.name as brand, 
m.name as model, 
l.registration_no,
to_char(br.created_at,'YYYY-MM-DD')as report_date,
to_char(br.created_at,'HH24:MI')as report_time,
l.user_id as host_id, 
concat(u.first_name, ' ',u.last_name)as host_name,
u.email as host_email, 
u.phone_number as host_phone_num,
u.uuid as host_uuid,
b.user_id as guest_id, 
concat(u2.first_name, ' ',u2.last_name)as guest_name,
br.user_id,
translate(br.comment, E'\n\r', ' ')as comment1,
case when brm.media is null then 'No'
else 'Yes' end as photos_attached,
case when br.user_id = l.user_id then 'host'
when br.user_id = b.user_id then 'guest'
else 'error' end as type,
CASE WHEN translate(br.comment, E'\n\r', ' ') ILIKE ('%accident%') OR
          translate(br.comment, E'\n\r', ' ') ILIKE ('%langgar%') OR
          translate(br.comment, E'\n\r', ' ') ILIKE ('%kemalangan%') OR
          translate(br.comment, E'\n\r', ' ') ILIKE ('%eksiden%') OR
          translate(br.comment, E'\n\r', ' ') ILIKE ('%late%') OR
          translate(br.comment, E'\n\r', ' ') ILIKE ('%lambat%') OR
          translate(br.comment, E'\n\r', ' ') ILIKE ('%return%')
     THEN 'Accident or late return'
     ELSE 'Non-Accident'
END AS report_type
from bookings b 
left join listings l on l.id = b.listing_id
left join booking_reports br on b.id = br.booking_id and br.user_id = l.user_id
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
left join users u2 on u2.id = b.user_id
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = b.listing_id
left join models m on m.id = l.model_id
left join brands bra on bra.id = m.brand_id
left join 
(select distinct brm.booking_report_id as media
from booking_report_media brm) brm on brm.media = br.id
where ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and br.comment is not null
--and b.ref_no = 'KKPH6SGL'
--and b.listing_id in (20035)
and br.created_at between (NOW() - interval'1 days') and NOW()
order by 8 desc
--limit 3
